abstract: As traditional retailers fade in the era of Amazon, a vacant department store near Washington becomes a refuge for people struggling to find affordable places to live.
snippet: As traditional retailers fade in the era of Amazon, a vacant department store near Washington becomes a refuge for people struggling to find affordable places to live.
lead_paragraph: ALEXANDRIA, Va. — Karleen Smith used to work at the Macy’s in Landmark Mall, putting price tags on summer dresses, housewares and the latest styles of shoes.

abstract: The inspector general, Michael E. Horowitz, has navigated a tricky role in Washington while maintaining his independence.
snippet: The inspector general, Michael E. Horowitz, has navigated a tricky role in Washington while maintaining his independence.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — In the office of Attorney General Jeff Sessions hangs a portrait of his predecessor Edwin Meese III, the Reagan-era conservative. Near the desk of the deputy attorney general is a painting of former Attorney General John Ashcroft, who pressed to expand the Justice Department’s powers after Sept. 11.

abstract: This remake of a 1972 film focuses on the drug trade and the pursuit of wealth in Atlanta.
snippet: This remake of a 1972 film focuses on the drug trade and the pursuit of wealth in Atlanta.
lead_paragraph: The American Dream is invoked several times in “Superfly.” The mentions come from the movie’s lead character, and from a song on the soundtrack. These days, it seems, the phrase is often used ironically. It’s all about the accumulation of wealth and a sybaritic lifestyle. There’s no spiritual dimension, no sense of genuine civic aspiration.

headline_main: Review: ‘Superfly’ Adds Bling to an Old Tale
headline_print_headline: Bringing Bling to a Dark Story of the Streets

abstract: The state ethics panel’s decision on the accusations against Sam Hoyt drew immediate questions about the body’s qualifications and independence.
snippet: The state ethics panel’s decision on the accusations against Sam Hoyt drew immediate questions about the body’s qualifications and independence.
lead_paragraph: ALBANY — A New York State ethics panel cleared a former aide to Gov. Andrew M. Cuomo of sexual harassment, seven months after a woman had publicly accused the aide, Sam Hoyt, of threatening and groping her.

abstract: The deaths, destruction and federal government’s response to the devastating storm provided a grim backdrop to the annual celebration.
snippet: The deaths, destruction and federal government’s response to the devastating storm provided a grim backdrop to the annual celebration.
lead_paragraph: In the beginning, and the middle, and the end, as always, there was the Puerto Rican flag: countless thousands of them waving as the National Puerto Rican Day Parade marched and danced up Fifth Avenue in Manhattan on Sunday in the steady drizzle, flags worn as ponchos, flags adorning T-shirts and hats and flip-flops.

abstract: “The Band’s Visit” won 10 awards, including best musical, and “Harry Potter and the Cursed Child” won best play. Students from Parkland, Fla., gave a surprise performance.
snippet: “The Band’s Visit” won 10 awards, including best musical, and “Harry Potter and the Cursed Child” won best play. Students from Parkland, Fla., gave a surprise performance.
lead_paragraph: • “The Band’s Visit,” a delicate musical about an Egyptian police orchestra stranded for a night in Israel, swept the awards, winning 10 prizes including best new musical.

abstract: Despite blustery rhetoric from politicians who have sought to make tax reforms a ballot issue for New Yorkers, many voters seem indifferent.
snippet: Despite blustery rhetoric from politicians who have sought to make tax reforms a ballot issue for New Yorkers, many voters seem indifferent.
lead_paragraph: In the months since the Republican overhaul of the federal tax code, New Yorkers have seen widespread perplexity, frantic revision of their state tax code — and a steady drumbeat of rhetoric from Democratic and Republican leaders who have vowed to use the plan as a rallying cry at the polls this fall.

abstract: Through clever planning and some negotiating, Chanet Tisdel and Chauncey Kearney managed to have a luxurious wedding on a budget.
snippet: Through clever planning and some negotiating, Chanet Tisdel and Chauncey Kearney managed to have a luxurious wedding on a budget.
lead_paragraph: The moment Chauncey Kearney broke out in a rash upon hearing the cost of flowers for his May 24 wedding was a moment of reckoning for his fiancée, Chanet Tisdel.

abstract: The bridge’s namesake had two Zs, but state officials included only one when it was christened in 1960. A new bill wants to change that.
snippet: The bridge’s namesake had two Zs, but state officials included only one when it was christened in 1960. A new bill wants to change that.
lead_paragraph: ALBANY — The Verrazano-Narrows Bridge: A colossal expanse linking Brooklyn and Staten Island, once the longest suspension bridge in the world and a proud symbol of New York City’s history and urban geography.
